"""
PART 3 Eligibility and assistance to be given

20. Value and form of a Scottish child payment

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-04-01.

(1)

The value of a Scottish child payment in respect of a child is £27.15 per week.
"""

person_is_child:
    entity: Person
    period: Week
    dtype: Boolean

scottish_child_payment_weekly_amount:
    entity: Person
    period: Week
    dtype: Money
    from 2025-04-01:
        if person_is_child: 27.15 else: 0
